Third-party attribution
=======================

This repository was bootstrapped from an earlier Cisco AP HomeRacker mount.
That original project was inspired by and used dimensions from:

- "Cisco AIR-AP-BRACKET-1" by nicba1010
- Thingiverse: https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:5491712
- Source file referenced locally as AIR-AP-BRACKET-1.scad
- Repo copy: third_party/thingiverse-5491712/AIR-AP-BRACKET-1.scad
- License: BSD license, as stated by the source model

The original AIR-AP-BRACKET-1.scad dimensions included the four Cisco AP
slider/keyhole cutouts and recessed two-layer slider-hole behavior. The current
Beryl AX HomeRacker sleeve source does not use that geometry in its active
OpenSCAD model, but this notice and the source copy are retained to preserve the
upstream attribution.
